            "title": "滬股收跌3點  全周升逾1.6%  深股收升  一周累升逾4%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">A股午後好轉，滬股一度倒升，惟收市報跌，深股收升89點，兩市成交合計24255.74億元(人民幣‧下同)。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240307_FI_source-ap_AShare-12.png.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240307_FI_source-ap_AShare-12.png.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">上證指數全日報4051，跌4點或0.1%，今早開報4043點，跌0.3%或12點，中段見4038點，跌17點或0.42%，為全日低位，其後跌幅收窄，午後曾倒升，見4058點，升3點或0.07%，為全日高位，半日成交10135.21億元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">深證成指全日報14885，升89點或0.6%，今早開報14806點，漲0.07%或10點。早段見14787，跌9點或0.06%，為全日低位，即反覆向上，午後高見14916，升120點或0.81%，為全日高位，全日成交14120.53元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">創業板指數全日升52點或1.43%，報3678點，今早開報3643點，漲0.47%或17點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">滬深300全日跌7點或0.17%，報4728點，今早開報4729點，跌0.16%或7點。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> 滬股一周升65點或1.63%，深股全周升576點或4.02%。</p>\n</div>",
